      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
